snippet.title: File Under Kingdom - Trailer
snippet.description:
File Under Kingdom
Coming January 18th
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1851120/File_Under_Kingdom/

File Under Kingdom is a mix of city builder, puzzle game, and interactive story. How you build the kingdom will alter events and/or influence the choices of its leaders. Use a variety of buildings to satisfy the kingdoms needs. See if you have what it takes to be the kings new Royal Planner.

Music: Owl Theory Music
